<D>__{i know what you mean. the pickin's are really gettin' slim. the whole strip is shrinking. ah, you know, i remember about five years ago, take you a couple of hours and a tank full of gas just to make one circuit. it was really somethin.'}
<A>__{suddenly, in the distance, there's a blood curdling scream from an incredible high performance engine. the entire drive in stops and listens.}
