<D>__{one fries grab it before i drop it.}
<A>__{she gives laurie an antagonistic look and goes off. steve laughs. laurie smiles. she's seventeen, very pretty, with big doe eyes, and a short bobbed hairdo. she pushes up the sleeves on steve's letterman sweater, which is sizes too large for her. his class ring glints on a chain around her neck. laurie is sweet, the image of vulnerability, but with a practical and self preserving mind beneath.}
